ps://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVIICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=bd13f143\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf</a><br />\n實體表格傳送門-&gt; 各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVIICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=6e853b6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n或公共屋邨辦事處<br />\n<a href=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201901%2F29%2FP2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVIICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=cbd62ffa\" target=\"_blank\">http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf</a><br />\n或選舉事務處(香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓/九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">交表</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVIICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=9319b7fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費傳真方法 </span></strong><br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / FAX.PLUS 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVIICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=1ec116db\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]"},{"pid":"f7fb230583a02274e90301e6dc1e8968aa9ad733","tid":1254400,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:10:02.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"1625d4635d0f928c23e41c86658e5b76f16d9ae1","tid":1254400,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66e2e969c15f783f17ec2cc535e9b6925cce8e2b","tid":1254400,"uid":70988,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:07:18.000Z","msg":"波台要人！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:13:30.000Z","msg":"波台有鳩硬sir撐住就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f51975c4cc1b521a3adf107e777d02d7112feb9e","tid":1254400,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T07:48:02.000Z","msg":"生做波台狗 死做cc人😤"},{"pid":"b16575813fd209476add16fc3bcbf37f1542099b","tid":1254400,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T07:51:57.000Z","msg":"me?"},{"pid":"a706bb170cd0eb749a09ffa1f78b6aa943c8d6c7","tid":1254400,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T07:55:45.000Z","msg":"大時大飛仲玩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a25ae3d653cee6b20a085d148fedb15987c964","tid":1254400,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T07:56:52.000Z","msg":"三毛又玩分化"},{"pid":"8799dbfe4858b5790067af4f4514f6c5e646357a","tid":1254400,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:02:50.000Z","msg":"推到呢個post 置頂就可以有幾萬人撐<br 